| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4678 — Recovery Inhibition (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c8e58dc3-c5e4-5fe0-8a48-a7c80eaeb523"
